text: Stuart Dutamby (born 24 April 1994) is a French sprinter. He competed in the men's 4 × 100 metres relay at the 2016 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:French male sprinters Category:Olympic athletes of France Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Saint-Germain-en-Laye Category:World Athletics Championships athletes for France
